summary: Small modification of Aela the Huntress, that still mantains her agressive appearance, but also gives her a lighter and prettier look.
descriptionHtml:
This is a small modification created in Skyrim NPC Editor that tries to change the appearance of Aela the Huntress NPC, mantaining most of the aspects of her original appearance, but giving her a more womanly look. In-game screenshots were taken along with CBBE and coverwomen. I recommend using both of them for better use.

If you have suggestions on how to improve this mod, please leave it in the comments section.
leotgo
author: leotgo
